  ;; ── Design notes ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
  (text "ES7243E AUDIO ADC NOTES (v1.1):\n\n1) Power:\n   AVDD = PVDD = 3V3_ANALOG (ultra-low noise LP2985-33)\n   DVDD = 3V3_MAIN\n   Separate AGND/DGND, star point at LP2985-33 output\n\n2) Single-ended input from SI4732:\n   LINP/RINP = signal via C17/C18 AC coupling + R6/R7+C19/C20 LPF\n   LINN/RINN = 0R to AGND\n   R8/R9 = 100k bias to VMID\n\n3) Anti-alias LPF: R=1k, C=10nF C0G → fc=15.9kHz\n   Adequate for Nyquist at 44.1kHz\n\n4) I2S slave mode:\n   BCLK=IO18, LRCK=IO19, SDOUT→I2S_DIN(IO21)\n   [FIXED] MCLK = I2S_MCLK → ESP32 IO0 output at 12.288MHz\n   ESP32 I2S driver: i2s_ll_set_mclk_src() + i2s_set_clk()\n   After boot IO0 is free to use as MCLK (no longer BOOT)\n\n5) I2C: addr 0x10 (AD0=GND), shared bus with SI4732\n\n6) References:\n   C_VMID/C_VREF: [FIXED] 0805→0603 10uF 6.3V X5R\n   Murata GRM188R60J106ME47D (0603 10uF 6.3V)\n\n[FIX LOG v1.1 - 2026-04-28]\n  BUG-01: MCLK pin floating → ES7243E PLL fail → no ADC output\n  FIX-01: I2S_MCLK global net added, connected to ESP32 IO0 (sheet 2)\n  BUG-02: C_VMID/C_VREF in 0805 (unnecessarily large)\n  FIX-02: Replaced with 0603 (10uF 6.3V X5R)"
    (at 200 100)
    (effects (font (size 1.7 1.7)) (justify left))
  )
)
